AUTOMATION SUITE DOCUMENTATION

Project Overview:
This project is a Python-based automation suite.

Modules:
- File Organizer
- Web Scraper
- Email Automation
- System Monitor

Setup:
Install required libraries:
pip install requests beautifulsoup4 schedule psutil

How to Run:
Run GUI using:
py gui_app.py

Code Structure:
Each module performs a specific automation task.

Features:
- Automation
- Scheduling
- GUI
- Logging

Conclusion:
This project demonstrates automation and integration using Python.